{"at":"2026-05-15T18:35:01.317Z","event":"stream_finished","streamId":"translation-article-llm-connection-strings-es-chunk-3-minimax-minimax-m2.5-nitro","phase":"translation","inputId":"article:llm-connection-strings:es:chunk-3","model":"openrouter/minimax/minimax-m2.5:nitro","durationMs":2511,"chunkCount":1,"textLength":351,"finalTextLength":351,"text":"### Anatomía de una Cadena de Conexión para LLMs\n\n![las partes de una cadena de conexión para LLMs](../inline-url-diagram-dark.svg)\n\nEl esquema es `llm://`. El host es la URL base de la API del proveedor. La ruta es el nombre del modelo. Y los parámetros de consulta manejan todas las opciones de tiempo de ejecución que usualmente ensucian tu código.","usage":{"inputTokens":2028,"inputTokenDetails":{"noCacheTokens":316,"cacheReadTokens":1712,"cacheWriteTokens":0},"outputTokens":472,"outputTokenDetails":{"textTokens":61,"reasoningTokens":411},"totalTokens":2500,"raw":{"prompt_tokens":2028,"prompt_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":1712,"cache_write_tokens":0,"audio_tokens":0,"video_tokens":0},"completion_tokens":472,"completion_tokens_details":{"reasoning_tokens":411,"image_tokens":0,"audio_tokens":0},"total_tokens":2500,"cost":0.00071256,"cost_details":{"upstream_inference_cost":0.00071256,"upstream_inference_prompt_cost":0.00014616,"upstream_inference_completions_cost":0.0005664},"is_byok":false},"reasoningTokens":411,"cachedInputTokens":1712},"providerMetadata":{"openrouter":{"usage":{"promptTokens":2028,"promptTokensDetails":{"cachedTokens":1712},"completionTokens":472,"completionTokensDetails":{"reasoningTokens":411},"cost":0.00071256,"totalTokens":2500,"costDetails":{"upstreamInferenceCost":0.00071256}},"provider":"Minimax","reasoning_details":[]}}}
